streamer_loyalty_rule_definition_average: Avg user watch time this month: The average watch time (not valid stream time) of users who entered the stream between the 1st of current month and yesterday.
streamer_loyalty_rule_definition_newfoll: New followers this month: Number of new followers calculated between the 1st of current month and yesterday, compared to last month.
streamer_loyalty_rule_definition_newpost: New posts this month: Number of new posts between the 1st of current month and yesterday, compared to last month.

New post shares this month: Number of times new posts were shared between the 1st of current month and yesterday. The figure counts all new post shares of the current month. Deleted posts will not be counted.
streamer_loyalty_rule_definition_points: Baby Coins received this month: Baby Coins received between the 1st of current month and yesterday.
streamer_loyalty_rule_definition_subscri: Army subscribers this month: Number of people in army (not newly added) between the 1st of current month and yesterday.
streamer_loyalty_rule_definition_uniqueg: Unique gift senders this month: Number of non-repeating gift senders between the 1st of current month and yesterday.
streamer_loyalty_rule_definition_uniquev: Unique viewers this month: Number of non-repeating viewers between the 1st of current month and yesterday.
streamer_loyalty_rule_definition_validst: Valid streamed days this month: Number of days with stream lengths qualifying as valid between the 1st of current month and yesterday.

Valid streamed hours this month: Total length of streams qualifying as valid between the 1st of current month and yesterday. A single stream must be longer than 30 minutes in length to be considered as valid. Maximum 2 valid streamed hours per day.

Valid streams this month: Number of streams with lengths qualifying as valid between the 1st of current month and yesterday. If a stream overlaps two months, it is counted towards the month it started in.
streamer_loyalty_rule_definition_watchin: Total watch hours this month: Total time the streamer was watched (not valid stream time) between the 1st of current month and yesterday.
streamer_loyalty_rule_detail1: Stream Level is assessed once a month. Every month is a new start, so keep up the good work to keep receiving awards and benefits. The higher your level, the more awards and benefits you'll get!
streamer_loyalty_rule_detail2: You'll receive the stream rewards and benefits in the following month. Use them before they expire or they will considered void.
